{"type": "email", "id": "email_001", "subject": "Weekly IT Department Meeting", "from": "kevin.wong@leesmarket.com", "from_name": "Kevin Wong", "to": ["linda.chen@leesmarket.com", "john.lee@leesmarket.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2021-10-02 08:00:00", "body": "Dear team,

Just a quick reminder about our weekly department meeting today at 3pm. We'll be discussing our ongoing projects and any issues you've been facing. Please prepare your updates beforehand.

Best,
Kevin", "folder": "inbox", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_002", "subject": "New Employee Onboarding", "from": "kevin.wong@leesmarket.com", "from_name": "Kevin Wong", "to": ["sarah.park@leesmarket.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2021-10-03 09:15:00", "body": "Hi Sarah,

I've heard we're getting some new hires next week. Can you please share the onboarding schedule with me? I want to ensure their IT systems are ready in time.

Thanks,
Kevin", "folder": "inbox", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_003", "subject": "Website Downtime", "from": "linda.chen@leesmarket.com", "from_name": "Linda Chen", "to": ["kevin.wong@leesmarket.com"], "cc": ["jackie.li@leesmarket.com"], "date": "2021-10-04 10:30:00", "body": "Hi Kevin,

We're planning a website update this weekend and there might be some downtime. Can you please inform the necessary teams and set up a notification for our customers?

Best,
Linda", "folder": "inbox", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_004", "subject": "Upcoming IT Audit", "from": "kevin.wong@leesmarket.com", "from_name": "Kevin Wong", "to": ["john.lee@leesmarket.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2021-10-05 11:45:00", "body": "Hi John,

Just a heads up, we have an IT audit scheduled for next month. I'll need your help to gather the necessary documents and logs. Let's meet next week to discuss the details.

Thanks,
Kevin", "folder": "inbox", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_005", "subject": "Product Recall Notice", "from": "michael.kim@leesmarket.com", "from_name": "Michael Kim", "to": ["kevin.wong@leesmarket.com"], "cc": ["jessica.tran@leesmarket.com", "david.nguyen@leesmarket.com"], "date": "2021-10-06 12:00:00", "body": "Hi Kevin,

We're issuing a recall for one of our products. We need IT's help to pull the sale records and notify the customers who purchased this item. Can you please assign someone to handle this?

Best,
Michael", "folder": "inbox", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_001", "subject": "IT Service Tickets for July 2025", "from": "kevin.wong@leesmarket.com", "from_name": "Kevin Wong", "to": ["linda.chen@leesmarket.com", "jackie.li@leesmarket.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2025-08-01 09:30:00", "body": "Hi Linda and Jackie,

I hope you're both well. I just wanted to provide an update on the number of IT tickets we received in July 2025. We had a total of 14 tickets specifically related to the development and troubleshooting of the gluten-free dumpling filter in our online store.

Let's ensure we track these numbers closely as we continue to enhance our online services, keeping in mind our goal to reduce service desk dependency and improve resolution times. This is critical to our larger objective of enhancing both employee and customer experience.

Best,
Kevin", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_002", "subject": "Re: IT Service Tickets for July 2025", "from": "linda.chen@leesmarket.com", "from_name": "Linda Chen", "to": ["kevin.wong@leesmarket.com", "jackie.li@leesmarket.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2025-08-01 10:05:00", "body": "Hi Kevin,

Thanks for the update. It's good to know that our team is proactively addressing these issues and working towards reducing dependency on the service desk. Let's continue to monitor these numbers closely in the coming months.

Best,
Linda", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
{"type": "email", "id": "email_003", "subject": "Re: IT Service Tickets for July 2025", "from": "jackie.li@leesmarket.com", "from_name": "Jackie Li", "to": ["kevin.wong@leesmarket.com", "linda.chen@leesmarket.com"], "cc": [], "date": "2025-08-01 11:00:00", "body": "Hi Kevin and Linda,

Thank you for the update. This information is certainly helpful as we plan our IT self-service strategy. Based on the number of tickets, it is clear that we need to strengthen our IT self-service capabilities to manage requests more efficiently. Let's continue this discussion in our next meeting.

Best,
Jackie", "folder": "sent", "read": true, "attachments": []}
